*******************  New storage policy on /work *********************
**********************************************************************
From January 1st, 2021, an automatic deletion policy on /work 
(alias ~/wt) will delete all files older than 90 days to prevent 
filling of the file system.
Please review your data below /work and save necessary data 
elsewhere as soon as possible.
In case of problems or questions please contact the HPC support team.
**********************************************************************
